sting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999886035768, \"rank\": 1.1396314431282066e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Ioannis Filippatos, the former Chair of the IBA Medical Committee, was adamant that the fighters should not be competing as women, stating \\\"Medicine is knowledge, it is not opinion,\\\" and adding \\\"The nature and the biological world do not change.\\\"\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both the fighters in question have won every single round they have fought in the games.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"XY chromosome Olympic boxers Lin Yu-Ting and Imane Khelif, described as \\\"male\\\" by the International Boxing Association, have both won every single round they have been in during the games and are now both one 'match' away from gold medals.\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.881774552290624, \"rank\": 0.13407672902572335, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 2903, \"end\": 2914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-Ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 2919, \"end\": 2931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0