sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7464197761443273e-19, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the push for \\\"genes are the only and hard truth\\\", then we pigeon hole ourselves.The biggest question here is that Swyer Syndrome occurs in 1 in 80,000 women( I am going to say women since most still have a functional womb and develop breasts), so two at the Olympics is a 0.00000156% chance.\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4274, \"end\": 4288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_gonadal_dysgenesis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swyer Syndrome\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_gonadal_dysgenesis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_gonadal_dysgenesis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Basically impossible.I would like a dialogue about that.\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You would like \\\"a dialogue about that\\\"?\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's your problem\\u2026  Everyone else is sick of debating genetic X-files scenarios.\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ok, so is a human with XY chromosomes and female genitalia a man and a human with XX chromosomes  and male genitalia a woman?\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4658, \"end\": 4672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 4717, \"end\": 4719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7